Two adults and a 13-year-old child were found dead in a veld outside an estate near Centurion this morning.The ages of the two adults could not be confirmed due to the brutality of their injuries.&nbsp;All three were declared dead on the scene.According to ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring, it appears that the three patients were bound, gagged, and burned to death."Police will investigate and post-mortems will be conducted to determine what exactly happened." said Meiring.Gauteng police spokesperson Captain Kay Makhubela could not immediately comment.http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/2-adults-teen-found-bound-gagged-and-burnt-to-death-in-veld-20170605